Package: cert-agent
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, redis-server (>= 6.0), systemd
Recommends: redis-tools
Description: mTLS Certificate Management Service with gRPC
 cert-agent is a modern service for managing mTLS certificates with automatic
 renewal, Redis-based tracking, and gRPC API for easy integration.
 .
 Features:
  * gRPC API for certificate management
  * Redis integration for certificate tracking
  * Automatic certificate renewal
  * mTLS certificate generation
  * Certificate revocation support
  * Real-time monitoring and notifications

Package: cert-agent-dev
Architecture: amd64 arm64
Depends: cert-agent (= ${binary:Version}), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Development files for cert-agent
 This package contains development files and examples for building
 clients that integrate with cert-agent gRPC API.
